의존성 추가
<dependency>
   <groupId>org.postgresql</groupId>
   <artifactId>postgresql</artifactId>
</dependency>

PostgreSQL 설치 및 서버 실행 (docker)
    docker run -p 5432:5432 -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=pass -e POSTGRES_USER=sangmoon -e POSTGRES_DB=springboot --name postgres_boot -d postgres

    docker exec -i -t postgres_boot bash

    su - postgres

    psql springboot

