    SELECT * FROM account;

PostgreSQL 경고 메시지
경고 :  org.postgresql.jdbc.PgConnection.createClob() is not yet implemented 해결 :  spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.jdbc.lob.non_contextual_creation=true